metadata.description: Marwynn Holdings, Inc. is a holding company operating through its subsidiaries, FuAn Enterprise, Inc. and Grand Forest Cabinetry Inc. The company specializes in supply chain solutions, offering food, snacks, non-alcoholic beverages, kitchen cabinets, flooring, and home improvement products. It also provides supply chain consulting and market expansion support services. Marwynn Holdings was incorporated in 2024 and is based in Irvine, California.
